TEXT.S: = Cicala'ay = Gaga mniq Taytung Cusangsyang ka alang Cicala'ay. 537 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 1,368 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 23% niqan 309 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 77% niqan 1,059 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis18%, Bunun2%, Paiwan1%, ni rahuq na o1%.
